                    int id,

                    int from,
                    byte[] value,
                    java.lang.Object proof)
Creates a paxos message. Used by the message factory to create a COLLECT or PROPOSE message TODO: Q tal meter isto sem quantificador, para ser so visivel no mesmo package?

Parameters:
paxosType - This should be MessageFactory.COLLECT or MessageFactory.PROPOSE
id - Consensus's execution ID
round - Round number
from - This should be this process ID
value - This should be null if its a COLLECT message, or the proposed value if it is a PROPOSE message
proof - The proof to be sent by the leader for all replicas

from - This should be this process ID
value - The value decided, or strongly/weakly accepted
